data.eml:eml: An annotated type catalogue of the camel spiders (Arachnida: Solifugae) held in the Zoological Museum Hamburg

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Harms, Danilo, Dupérré, Nadine (2018): An annotated type catalogue of the camel spiders (Arachnida: Solifugae) held in the Zoological Museum Hamburg. Zootaxa 4375 (1): 1-58, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4375.1.1
